\c 8
\s Jehovha anoshoora Israeri nezvifananidzo zvake
\p
\v 1 Hwamanda pamuromo wako. \add Achauya\add* segondo kurwisa imba yaJehovha, nokuti vakadarika sungano yangu, nekutadzira murairo wangu.
\v 2 Vachadana kwandiri \add vachiti\add*: Mwari wangu, isu Israeri tinokuzivai.
\v 3 Israeri wakarasa zvakanaka. Muvengi achamuteverera.
\v 4 Vakagadza madzimambo, asi pasina ini; vakamisa machinda asi ini ndisingazvizivi; pasirivha yavo negoridhe ravo vakazviitira zvifananidzo, kuti vagurwe.
\p
\v 5 Mhuru yako, iwe Samariya, yaka\add ku\add*rasa; kutsamwa kwangu kwakavapfutira; kusvika rini pavachazokwanisa kuva vasina mhosva?
\v 6 Nokuti ichi chakabvawo kuna Israeri; mupfuri wakachiita, uye hachisi Mwari; asi mhuri yeSamariya ichava mafufu.
\v 7 Nokuti vanodzvara mhepo, zvino vachakohwa chamupupuri, hakungavi nezviyo zvimire; chipande hachingabudisi upfu; kana chichibereka, vatorwa vachazvimedza.
\v 8 Israeri wakamedzwa; zvino vava pakati pevechirudzi semudziyo usina chinofadza pauri.
\v 9 Nokuti ivo vakakwira kuAsiriya, mbongoro yesango yega pachayo. Efuremu wakahaya vadiwa.
\v 10 Hongu, kunyange vakahaya pakati pevechirudzi, ikozvino ndichavaunganidza; zvino vachatanga kutapudzwa nokuda kwemutoro waJehovha newemachinda.
\v 11 Nokuti wakatadzisa aritari dzangu, aritari dzichava kwaari dzekutadza.
\v 12 Ndakamunyorera zvinhu zvikuru zvemurairo wangu, \add asi\add* zvakaverengwa sechinhu chevatorwa.
\v 13 \add Kana zviri\add* zvibairo zvezvipiriso zvangu, vanobaira nyama, ndokudya, Jehovha haafadzwi nazvo. Ikozvino acharangarira zvakaipa zvavo, nekushanyira zvivi zvavo. Vachadzokera kuEgipita.
\v 14 Nokuti Israeri wakakanganwa Muiti wake, ndokuvaka matembere, uye Judha wakawanza maguta akashoshewa, asi ndichatuma moto pamusoro pemaguta ake, uye uchapedza mizinda yawo.